title: Eisenhower National Historic Site: Bookstore
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Bookstore            Bookstore      The Eisenhower NHS Bookstore is open from 9am to 5pm.  The Bookstore is operated by Event Network.  Merchandise may be ordered by phone at (717) 338-9114 Ext. 4418 Eisenhower NHS Bookstore Event Network 1195 Baltimore Pike Gettysburg, PA 17325
